snippet.title: SNK 40th ANNIVERSARY COLLECTION - Street Smart & Prehistoric Isle in 1930 (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://snk40th.com/
Pre-order today! http://bit.ly/SNK40th
Available for Nintendo Switch, November 13

Whether you are traveling to the far off Bermuda Triangle in Prehistoric Isle in 1930 or bringing a fighting tournament to its knees in SNK's first ever fighting game in Street Smart, this collection is packed full of SNK firsts! Get these previously arcade-only titles now for your Nintendo Switch! 

The arcade comes home in this amazing collections from the earliest titles in SNK's illustrious catalog. Celebrating 40 years of titles that changed the landscape of arcade and console libraries across the world, available for the first time in one collection! 

Pixel-perfect and chocked full of special features like saving anywhere and rewind, all with an enormous gallery of rare and detailed production notes and materials. Take the arcade with you wherever you go with the definitive early SNK arcade collection!
